The paper describes a machine learning system for time-series anomaly detection, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The system also involves detecting anomalies in data, which could fall under the category of computer security and cryptography (cs.CR) or social and information networks (cs.SI). Finally, the system involves processing and analyzing large amounts of data, which could fall under the category of data structures and algorithms (cs.DS).
